I"À&<h2 id="c-abstractinterface"><center>C# Abstract/Interface</center></h2>

<h3 id="--abstract--">- Abstract -</h3>
<ul>
  <li></li>
  <li>Edit <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_config.yml</code> file.</li>
  <li>Edit <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">index.md</code>.</li>
  <li>Edit <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_data/projects.yaml</code></li>
  <li>Add a logo with a small one to <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">images</code> folder. (eg. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">logo.png</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">logo-small.png</code>)</li>
  <li>Remove sample posts from <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_posts</code> folder and add yours.</li>
  <li>Remove/Change sample images from <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">images</code> folder.</li>
  <li>Change repo name to <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">YourUserName.github.io</code></li>
</ul>

<p>That‚Äôs all.</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Class Blog
{
  
  Console.WriteLine("GDGD");
} 
</code></pre></div></div>

